      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLUE TROMBONE (7) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 26.17. Draws out wide but in form and has the ability. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Great chance to get the job done again. ELEVATE (2) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (26.39) at Ballarat. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Expected to give a good account. DARNUM FOX (3) finds it hard to win. Finished third (26.56) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Solid record here winning three races. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Leading chance. FOUND TREASURE (8) can find the frame without surprising.",
